name: Desjardins American Equity Index ETF
longDescription: DMEU seeks to replicate the performance of the solactive  GBS United states 500 cad index. under normal conditions, etf will primarily invest in large & mid cap securities of American companies. The Desjardins American Equity Index ETF Seeks to replicate to the extent reasonably possible  before fee  expenses, the performance of an American equity index.
